cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with algorithmic approaches for tumor assessment, specifically for mitotic figure identification, using machine learning techniques. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses domain transfer and adaptation, which are topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the use of whole slide scanning microscopes is mentioned, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
